long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension showcases Greninja's iconic ninja-like presence, bringing action-packed vibes and a touch of mystique to your new tabs. Perfect for fans of Pokémon and its agile Water/Dark-type star!

Features:
🌊 A dynamic live wallpaper featuring Greninja in a striking ninja pose.
🌐 Customizable search bar for a personalized browsing experience.
🕒 Clock and date display for efficient time management.
🔗 Easy-to-navigate shortcuts to your favorite websites.
Enhance your browsing with Greninja's legendary finesse and captivating style!
